A mixed plugin for OpenComputer. Mixed plugins can ship any combination
of channels, providers, tools, and skills.

## Install

Copy this directory into one of:

- `~/.opencomputer/plugins/{{ plugin_id }}/` (global)
- `~/.opencomputer/profiles/<name>/plugins/{{ plugin_id }}/` (profile-local)

Or run `opencomputer plugin install <path-to-this-dir>`.

## Trim before shipping

This scaffold registers a channel adapter, a provider, AND a tool. If
your plugin only ships a subset, delete the files and `register()` lines
for the components you don't use.

